<slide title="PHP-SOAP">
<list title="The good parts">
<bullet>SOAP 1.1</bullet>
<bullet>C based Client and Server</bullet>
<bullet>RPC/Encoded only</bullet>
<bullet>HTTP and HTTPS only</bullet>
<bullet>Supports 1999/2001 Schema</bullet>
<bullet>WSDL Support</bullet>
<bullet>Fastest implementation available for PHP</bullet>
</list>
<list title="The bad parts">
<bullet>SOAP 1.1 and 1.2 support not finished</bullet>
<bullet>WSDL support not finished, cannot interop test</bullet>
<bullet>PHP 4 Object support</bullet>
<bullet>No streaming XML parser (yet)</bullet>
</list>
</slide>